objects.draw

Class PlanetShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • objects.draw.PlanetShape

  • public class PlanetShape
extends java.lang.Object
    Class represents set of functions added to given Planet which allows to draw it in ImgPlane. This class is practically drawable shape of the given planet with it's paths.
    Author:
    Martin Hamet
